<ArticleLayout
  title="Trauma-Informed Wealth Advisory — Understanding the Role of Trauma in Family Behavioral Health"
  description="How unresolved trauma shapes financial behavior, family dynamics, and treatment engagement in affluent families — and what advisors must understand to respond effectively."
  pillar="Integrated Family Wellness"
